Ajay Gupta hit back at radio journalist Steven Grootes slur that he (Gupta) is a liar.Gupta was responding to an article titled The interview I could not publish. Until now written by Grootes.Grootes said in the article: This was a tough interview, I threw everything I had at him. Some of his answers seem to have been blatant lies, particularly his claims around Van Rooyen and Zwane. In a statement Gupta said: It has come to our attention that Stephen Grootes reported on November 21, 2016 that Ajay Gupta lied pursuant to an interview conducted on February 16, 2016. Let it be recorded that Grootes s allegation is noted but categorically denied, the statement said. The rights of Ajay Gupta are reserved and appropriate steps will be taken against Grootes in the appropriate forum. Grootes is also invited to substantiate his false, defamatory claim. TNA Reporternews@thenewage.co.za